
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>


<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h1 class="card-title text-center">Privacy Policy <i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill"></i></h1>
            <p class="text-muted text-center">Effective date: October 9, 2024</p>

            <p>Welcome to our Privacy Policy page! We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This document explains how we collect, use, and safeguard the data you provide while using our website.</p>

            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect personal data that you provide directly to us when you sign up for our services, make a purchase, or interact with our website. This may include your name, email address, payment details, and other information necessary for the services we provide.</p>

            <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use your information to improve our services, process transactions, send notifications, and comply with legal obligations. Your data is never sold or shared with third parties without your consent.</p>

            <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
            <p>
                We use cookies to enhance your experience on our website. You can choose to disable cookies through your browser settings, but this may affect how our website functions.
                <button id="acceptCookies" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Accept Cookies</button>
            </p>

            <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement strong security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</p>

            <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
            <table id="userRightsTable" class="table table-striped table-bordered">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Right</th>
                        <th>Description</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Access</td>
                        <td>You have the right to request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Correction</td>
                        <td>You can request that we correct any inaccurate data.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Deletion</td>
                        <td>You have the right to request the deletion of your personal data.</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We reserve the right to update our Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

            <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@example.com">privacy@example.com</a>.</p>
             <h2>8. Say my name</h2>
             <p> My Name is ZingDragonVipProZZZ.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>